data.description: Great opportunity with this 2 Bedroom (study could be third bedroom) 2.5 Bath Townhome. Set on a Conservation Lot this home features Honey maple wood Kitchen cabinets, Granite countertops, Wood Flooring, inside laundry. The high ceilings are accentuated with Crown molding Throughout. Split bedroom plan with master on second floor. Study/Den located on first floor could function as third bedroom. Private Screened rear patio with view of conservation. New A/C installed 2022. Community pool and assigned parking. Seconds from the SunCoast parkway with easy commute to Tampa and surrounding areas.
